EARS TO ME raced off of the pace in the four path, but could not get involved today. AWESOME OUTLAW raced from the middle of the field, raced on the rail, saved ground, moved up on the inside through the turn, tired late. FURIOUS AVENGER raced off of the pace, raced on the rail but showed little today. MIRANDEN vied for the lead, raced in the two path, took command, set the pace, then stopped in the stretch.
